spremnih da me sjebu i
pokupe milion dolara,

182
00:14:33,624 --> 00:14:35,197
nemam ni trunku žaljenja.

183
00:14:37,687 --> 00:14:40,402
I iskreno, u dubini svog bica,
jako sam polaskan zbog toga.

184
00:14:51,857 --> 00:14:54,083
Ruže traže stalnu negu.

185
00:14:54,677 --> 00:14:55,514
Da.

186
00:14:55,787 --> 00:14:57,055
Tek ste se doselili?

187
00:14:57,089 --> 00:14:58,484
Da, juce.

188
00:14:58,959 --> 00:15:00,249
Jeste li amerikanac?

189
00:15:00,391 --> 00:15:01,251
Da.

190
00:15:02,633 --> 00:15:03,996
Dobro ili loše?

191
00:15:04,031 --> 00:15:06,569
Francuska je glavno odredište
za strance.

192
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,830
Hocete li ostati duže?

193
00:15:07,865 --> 00:15:10,347
Ne, ne ostajemo dugo na jednom mestu.
Mnogo putujemo.

194
00:15:10,582 --> 00:15:11,722
Zbog mog posla.

195
00:15:12,915 --> 00:15:13,726
Šta radite?

196
00:15:15,727 --> 00:15:16,720
Ja sam pisac.

197
00:15:17,391 --> 00:15:21,070
